Description: Wayland virtual keyboard for GNU/Linux with modifier key support
 Vboard is a lightweight, customizable on-screen keyboard designed for Linux systems with Wayland support.
 It includes modifier keys such as Ctrl, Alt, Tab and Super (Meta/Win) for desktop shortcuts and normal keyboard workflows.
